    "English": "A flexible upgrade circuit, compatible with all <span class=\"name name-stellar\">person Multi-Tools</span>.<br><br>This module can be wired into a Multi-Tool at a Space Station <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Multi-Tool Upgrade Rack</span>, granting the user more space in the Multi-Tool's internal layout to add further upgrades or technology specialisations.",
